@@@ PCL installation guide
@@@ VincentChan
@@@ 11/11/2020

1) Download pcl-1.8.1
$ wget https://codeload.github.com/PointCloudLibrary/pcl/zip/pcl-1.8.1

2) Build and install
$ cd pcl-1.8.1
$ mkdir build
$ cd build
$ cmake ..

3) Edit the build/features/ line10, delete pcl_2d-1.8
$ sudo make -j6
$ sudo make install
